    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "please don't edit `style.min.css` directly it is autogenerated. The max width is due to bootstrap, I know this might be annoying, but we don't have the bandwidth to support a too much modified (1170 is actually\n\n```\n.span (@columns) {\n      width: (@gridColumnWidth * @columns) + (@gridGutterWidth * (@columns - 1));\n   }\n```\n\nwith columns = 12.)\n"
  },
